title: Triumph
info:
Released: May 26, 2007. Format: 192Kbps MP3 created with ModPlug Tracker.

This tune is based on a song by skyscape/Libris of the same name, which was entered (aeons ago!) into Nifflas' 30-second compo. This is a dance/electronic tune, and might one day be released as a tune with my band.
